[05/06/2019 00:35:46] <font color="#ffffff">quemar combustible caro,</font>
[05/06/2019 00:35:56] <font color="#ffffff">sino fueloil residual.</font>
[05/06/2019 00:35:59] <font color="#ffff00">El llamado combustible de caldera,</font>
